text: Benno Wandolleck (18 April 1864 - 1930) was a German sports shooter and zoologist. He competed in the 30m team military pistol event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1864 births Category:1930 deaths Category:German male sport shooters Category:German zoologists Category:Olympic shooters of Germany Category:Shooters at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Gdańsk
